Take control of your VIEWING experience from your trusted premium ENTERTAINMENT COMPANY with the GOtv App today. Have a peace of mind knowing that you are in control!

The GOtv App is an easy and convenient way to MANAGE your GOtv account, FIX ERRORS, PAY online, CHANGE PACKAGES, UPDATE your details all from one place.

Wait, there’s more…Get access to the latest NEWS FROM AROUND THE WORLD, SPORTS GAMES TODAY and MOVIES NOW! Because we’ve also created a clever way for you to gain access to GOtv Now, ShowMax and BoxOffice. Now you can keep track of MOVIE SHOWTIMES, NEWS ALERTS and ARTICLES with ease! Anytime, Anywhere ...

WITH THE GOTV APP, YOU CAN:

• Check your balance: View how much you owe or have, pay your bills and always stay connected.
• Manage your account: This feature helps you manage your personal info, privacy settings, upload a profile photo and so much more.
• Upgrade or Downgrade Package: You are in control, satisfy your entertainment needs by exploring our GOtv ENTERTAINMENT PACKAGE CHANNELS.
• Privacy & Security: Your personal information is yours, so with this feature we help protect your information and details, all it takes is just a single click to switch this feature on. Login to your accounts and manage your viewing remotely with the comfort of knowing your information is safe.
• Retrieve details: You can easily recover your Smartcard number if you have forgotten it by using the App.
• Fix Errors: Which Error code is on your screen? Easily fix common errors on your GOtv decoder to stay watching. What’s even better is that you don’t need to login onto the App to fix errors on your decoder.

Now that’s convenience on another level...

GOtv - It’s your account, on your terms!
Great ENTERTAINMENT, DAILY NEWS, KIDS MOVIES and your favorite SPORTS GAMES for you and your entire family.
